<p class="bold">Shw'mae! Welcome</p>
<p>Isn't it lush? This is a relaxed space, for people who need it. I've noticed through the years how Theatr Clwyd embraces everyone – whatever your age, ability or circumstance. You're all part of the family.</p>
<p>This box is at the back of the theatre, at the far right. It has a big rectangular window, looking out at the stage and the gorgeous theatre seats. Hey, audience, we're behind you!</p>
